{
  "stem": "25639.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at the slightest provocation, that dog would just climb up on us and-- and mar us, and just tear us to pieces.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were-- I believe there were two guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I only remember two, who were placed in front of the barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, remember, this was not the setting of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a city, which was terribly-- suffered terribly from-- from bombardments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And our job was to open up the major streets of bombarded debris, so the German artillery and vehicles could pass through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Once in a while, on our way to work, we-- we would encounter some kind civilians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember one time, a little old lady-- her hair was up in a bun here, and sort of graying, and she had this huge French-- French bread under-- tucked under her arm-- and her hair-- head was sort of stooped.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she looked this way and that way, and she was just waiting for the right time for her to throw us that bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it felt so good that there was-- there are some human beings out there who care about us, and who risked their life-- lives for us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Something funny happened on our job once, which I'd like to share.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One time, we-- we were lined up in a different sort of way on this very wide boulevard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were divided into small groups of four, or five, or six of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I think it was five or six.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, and so the-- the couple of guards just went back and forth in a long area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So it gave us a little chance to, sort of, see what else is there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
